 	This is a pixel graphics class library called Raster.  It is designed
for device and host independence. 

The classes in this library are:

RasterColor		A color (device-independent).
RasterValue		An integral value of a pixel (32-bit min.)
RasterLUT		A table of color values
 RasterLUTCore		A LUT in core memory
 RasterLUTVGA		A LUT for VGA device
RasterPosition		An integral x-y coordinate pair
 RasterSize		""

Raster			The base class for all rasters.
 RasterDevice
  RasterDeviceVGA
   RasterDeviceV7VRAM
 RasterMemory		An in-core raster
  RasterMemory8
  RasterMemory24
 RasterFile		The base class for rasters stored in a file.
  RasterFile8
  RasterFile24

